recreateDataset

public void recreateDataset(GenreList genres,
                            java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> features)
The Instances object that defines the dataset is defined transient, since it also contains bulky training data that becomes problematic if serialized. This method recreates the dataset definition without adding training data. It's designed for use in reconstituting an ensemble of models.

Parameters:
genres - Genre list associated with model.
features - List of features from model.normalizer.
